Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
Description: Package to fit probabilistic models to estimate customer lifetime value (CLV).
    It includes fast and accurate implementations of buy-'til-you-die models in 
    non-contractual settings (e.g., retail business). with and without time-invariant and time-varying covariates. Currently, the package includes the 
    Pareto/NBD model, the GGompertz/NBD model for the purchase and the attrition processes as well as the Gamma/Gamma model for the spending process.
